{"tid":575614,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇熟悉勞工法例的巴打/絲打可以打救一下我？","createTime":"2018-02-28T10:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T05:11:12.000Z","uid":167445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5eff22fade0aefb10b6240c2e0f01434f113bc8f","tid":575614,"uid":167445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n收左一封警句信比人炒9左，連代通知金都唔比，點搞啊<br />\n<br />\n已上勞仔，依舊唔比啊<br />\n<br />\n炒人理由如下：<br />\n玩手機 打錯文件 覆少左email 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d324cd9b082b887de73b3d72e8f1728cafd974f","tid":575614,"uid":82175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"警句信 <br />\n我明你點解俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78306084e3182fc95ffdbf6f37c37c5ba234c5a4","tid":575614,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"可否即時解僱僱員而不付代通知金？<br />\n<br />\n理論上是可以的，但需符合以下條件，如果僱員在工作上：<br />\n<br />\n故意不服從僱主合法合理的命令；<br />\n行爲不當；<br />\n欺詐、不忠實；或<br />\n慣常疏忽職責<br />\n<br />\n佢咁樣算當你係慣常疏忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}